Description:
Love this modern and sleek north-facing haven
Ideal as a brilliant investment or suited for anyone wanting to live in the stylish H1 complex right in the heart of the NewQuay precinct, this modern and relaxed 1 bedroom apartment is an unmissable opportunity! This striking building offers fantastic facilities which include a library lounge, media room, and gym.
Features an enviable northerly aspect
Open living and meals zone boasts fantastic natural light
North-facing balcony is a superb space to enjoy the great outdoors
Stone kitchen features quality stainless steel appliances
Bedroom with built-in robe storage
Well-appointed bathroom with designer fittings
European laundry
Ducted heating and cooling
Secure intercom entry
Secure car space
This stellar location has you so close to The District Docklands which has a state of the art entertainment precinct including Hoyts Cinemas and in mid-2019 will be home to a fresh food precinct with butchers, delis, bakeries, and coffee roasters. Youre also near Marvel Stadium, Capital City Bike Trail, easy access to leading universities including University of Melbourne and RMIT University, CBD bound trams, and simple access to the Skybus taking you to Melbourne Airport.
Please contact Vicky Leong on 0452 486 860 to arrange an inspection.

Description:
Delivering Stunning Docklands Style in Nolan Tower
With an outstanding position a stones throw to NewQuay Promenade and Victoria Harbour, and the perfect choice for astute investors or owner-occupiers, this well-appointed one bedroom apartment has everything you could ever need from a Docklands residence.
The full-length balcony is a terrific outdoor space with access from the living zone and bedroom, while the tiled kitchen boasts large bench space and stainless steel splashback as well as appliances including a dishwasher.
Superb north-facing living particularly in the open and spacious lounge and meals hub is a true highlight, while the bedroom has ample storage with built in robes running the full length of the room. Dont forget the designer marble bathroom, European laundry, intercom, car space, storage cage and access to the gym and pool as other extras.
Within the free tram zone and moments to Southern Cross Station, Etihad Stadium, Harbour Town Shopping Centre, local cafes and eateries the location could not be more convenient.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0437092078 to arrange an exclusive inspection

Description:
BEST VALUE FOR MONEY APARTMENT IN DOCKLANDS!!
This spacious one bedroom apartment is situated on the 4th level in the popular Soho Apartments in the heart of the business and sports precinct at Docklands.
Featuring formal entry, a good size bedroom with BIR's, open plan living area leading off to a decent size balcony overlooking the new Channel Nine building towards the city with a lovely light filled easterly aspect.
Kitchen is quite well equipped with quality appliances and stone bench top finishes and the bathroom is modern and bright with neutral colour tones.
Total area is approx. 60 sqm including the balcony area.
Location is absolutely electric too!
Situated right in the middle of the business and sports precinct amongst cafes and bars and right across the street from Etihad Stadium so it could easily be a great little weekender where you can stroll across to Etihad and watch your favourite team win and then off to a local restaurant for dinner and drinks to celebrate!!
Car park leased at $261PCM up to 2017.
Vacant possession is available if required as of 1st May this year, so you can move in anytime(subject to giving 65 days notice to the current tenant.
If you work in the CBD, its just a few minutes walk to Spencer Street and over to Bourke Street to access the CBD and ideal if your work is based in Docklands.
From an investment perspective, this building is very popular, well located and quite easy to lease quality apartments in and is definitely an established residential destination amongst corporate personnel which include the banking, finance, IT and insurance sectors in the immediate vicinity.
Current rental is at $1716 PCM till 01/05/2019 which does not including car park.
INSPECT AS ADVERTISED. CONTACT AGENT FOR FURTHER DETAILS.
Call SUNNY LU on 0422 060 234 / 0434 183 780.

Description:
Invest or live in this brand new corner retreat
Blending contemporary luxury with a low-maintenance floorplan, this brand new one bedroom corner apartment in the exclusive Marina Tower is the perfect entry level buy for keen investors who want to dip their toes in the Docklands waters.
Also great for first home buyers who will appreciate the allure of this appealing area, youll love the amazing highlights that come with this 15th floor gem. Features breathtaking harbour views from the east-facing balcony, relaxed and bright living/meals with northern views including the Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, stone kitchen with Miele appliances, bedroom with mirrored built-in robe storage, elegant bathroom, European laundry, reverse cycle cooling, and secure intercom.
Marina Tower has some of the best facilities in the NewQuay precinct including a lavish lobby lounge, library, private business centre, meeting rooms, cinema, lounge and billiard room, kitchen and dining area, rooftop pool, gym, and expansive deck. Location wise, youre in close proximity to the popular The District Docklands, Ron Barassi Snr Park, Marvel Stadium, waterfront restaurants, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, and trams.
To book an inspection please contact Vicky Leong on 0452 486 860 or Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556.

Description:
Live in style in this exceptional Yarra Point abode
This excellent 11th floor residence is an ideal choice for owner-occupiers and investors alike. The light-filled and relaxed central living and meals provides a sizeable area suited for morning breakfasts and lazing in front of the TV after a long day at work. This zone further opens out to a long balcony where you can enjoy summer sunsets with wine or beer in hand.
The stone kitchen has a high end feel with luxe benchtops, moveable island bench, and stainless steel Miele appliances. Both bedrooms are equipped with built-in robes and are in close proximity to the gorgeous bathroom, meanwhile further embrace a European laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, secure car space, and access to RekDek with gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna.
Surrounded by green parklands, youll love this stunning Yarras Edge precinct close to South Wharf Promenade with restaurants and bars, local eateries including Bangpop, Citizen Café and Bar, and Munich Brauhaus just to name a few. Youre also not far from DFO shopping, Crown Casino, Southbank Promenade, great Southbank, CBD, and South Melbourne attractions, trams, and Southern Cross Station.

Description:
Stunning bay views from this brilliant Collins Street abode
A stylish and elegant example of Docklands living right on the 19th floor of the excellent 883 Collins residential complex, this wonderful 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment has a riverside location that will be impossible to ignore.
Bright light fills the open and spacious lounge and dining zone, with full sliding doors opening out to a south-facing balcony which promises brilliant views of Port Phillip Bay. The kitchen is a further addition to this main living space and is highlighted by a sublime stone benchtop and quality stainless steel Miele appliances.
Both bedrooms feature the southerly aspect with gorgeous bay vistas, including the master bedroom which also comes with a sleek ensuite and walk-in robe. Other extras include a pristine main bathroom, European laundry, split system heat/cool, secure intercom, and secure car space. You also have access to a 20m swimming pool, cinema, billiards room, gym, yoga studio, private dining room, residents lounge, and landscaped BBQ deck.
Make the most of this amazing Victoria Harbour precinct location which is near Buluk Park, Docklands Park, Woolworths supermarket, local cafes, Library at the Dock, The Hub @ Docklands, and trams down Collins Street.

Description:
Stunning waterside living in the Palladio
Enjoy a modern and relaxed harbourside way of living with this exceptional 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment in the inspired Palladio residential complex in the NewQuay precinct.
Beautiful timber floors through living, kitchen & bedrooms
Relaxed lounge/meals opens out to generous balcony with stunning water views
Fantastic modern kitchen includes breakfast bar and stainless steel appliances
Master bedroom includes a deluxe ensuite
Both bedrooms with built-in robe storage
Sleek central bathroom sits next to the handy European laundry
Reverse cycle heating and cooling
Additional wall heating in bedrooms
Secure intercom entry
Secure car space
AMENITIES
The fantastic Palladio complex which has a design by renowned Fender Katsalidis allows residents access to an exclusive health club featuring rooftop pool, private function area, and fully-equipped gymnasium with breathtaking views.
LOCATION
There is so much to enjoy in the NewQuay precinct, from brilliant waterside restaurants including Fish Bar, Renzos Bar, and Bhoj, to Marvel Stadium for footy fans, Capital City Bike Trail, and access to the vibrant food and entertainment hub that is The District Docklands which has Hoyts Cinemas and so much more. Accessibility to the rest of Melbourne and some of the citys best universities is also taken care of thanks to nearby free trams, Southern Cross Station, and the Skybus service to Melbourne Airport.
Please contact Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

BEST WATERFRONT LIVING!!
A rare offering is this superb three bedroom apartment perched high on the 17th floor enjoying sunny North facing the water views.
Located in the luxurious 'Convesso', this 5 star building has set the benchmark for all future living within the Docklands precinct. The views from this beautiful apartment could not be better as you peer from your living room or main bedroom across the water to Newquay and beyond, the marina below or down the river to the Bolte Bridge. STUNNING TOP FLOOR BAY VIEWS

Description:
Cutting-Edge Class in Unbeatable Harbourside Location
Embrace a unique, dual-key opportunity with this perfect pair of style-focused apartments sharing breathtaking views stretching across the stunning city skyline to the blissful, blue waters of Victoria Harbour. Together on the one title in a superbly central city-edge location, this inviting package comprising a 1 bedroom apartment plus a separate studio apartment offers enticing possibilities. Think outside the box and enjoy a waterfront lifestyle with celebrated restaurants, convenient supermarket shopping, and free CBD trams all on your doorstep.
Set sky-high on the 27th floor of the sought-after Victoria Point complex, discover 2 apartments with a welcoming shared entry. The 1 bedroom entertainer will impress from the very first step inside with imposing walls of floor-to-ceiling glass revealing a striking day and night panorama, touching on Victoria Harbour, Marvel Stadium, Bolte Bridge, and the Melbourne Wheel. Capturing northern sun with ease, discover far-reaching, open-plan living and dining, complemented by a Caesarstone kitchen with quality stainless-steel appliances. Step outside to an enclosed balcony or winter garden and a second private, bedroom balcony overlooking Marvel Stadium and the city skyline. The studio apartment shares the same revealing stadium views and features a streamlined Caesarstone-topped kitchen with integrated microwave, fridge, gas cooktop and glossy splashback.
Ideal as a city base or investment option, both apartments offer a double concealed laundry with Fisher and Paykel dryer, a fully tiled bathroom with stone-topped vanity, ducted heating/cooling, roller blinds, mirrored built-in robes, and double-glazing. Take advantage of secure parking plus storage cage, video intercom entry, on-site building manager, concierge, and exclusive access to resort-style facilities including a fully equipped gym and heated pool. Easy to love, exceptional to live in and effortless to rent out, just one inspection will convince that you are in the presence of something special!
* Photo identification will be required upon entering the property at the inspection time.

Description:
A DUAL LEVEL TO DESIRE AT DOCK 5
Situated on the podium level of the prestigious Dock 5 complex sits this sumptuous split level loft style apartment. Comprising of 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom, a large living zone, and an abundance of natural light, this modern city home is sure impress with its location, price and charm.
Enter on the first floor to the generous living room and classy kitchen, which includes stainless steel Smeg appliances and plenty of cupboard space. Floor to ceiling windows open up on to the large balcony with lovely views of Victoria Harbour.
Ascending to the second level presents enhanced views of Victoria Harbour from the bedroom, along with built in robes in the large bedroom, and a chic bathroom with Euro-laundry. Rounding out this Docklands gem is split system heating/cooling, secure swipe/intercom entry, secure car space and access to the pool and gymnasium.
All this only moments from an array of harbour side restaurants, Marvel Stadium, public transport, bike tracks, world class shopping, and access to Citylink.

Description:
BEST WATERFRONT LIVING!!
A rare offering is this superb three bedroom apartment perched high on the 17th floor enjoying sunny North facing the water views.
Located in the luxurious 'Convesso', this 5 star building has set the benchmark for all future living within the Docklands precinct. The views from this beautiful apartment could not be better as you peer from your living room or main bedroom across the water to Newquay and beyond, the marina below or down the river to the Bolte Bridge. "Beautiful by day, Fantastic by Night."
This stylish apartment comprises of three spacious bedrooms, a designer kitchen, stone bench tops, refrigerator and an abundance of cupboard space, living room with amazing water views, a wide balcony perfect for entertaining or relaxing, two boutique hotel style bathrooms, ducted air conditioning and heating, two secure undercover car spaces and a storage cage.
In addition, the amenities in this luxurious building includes are a 24-hour concierge, residents lounge, Business Centre & Board Room, Cinema (within the Concavo building), North facing Sky Garden facing the water, with BBQ facilities, 25-meter pool, spa and sauna, gymnasium and treatment room.
Don't miss a fantastic opportunity to secure this apartment right by the waterside!
